file: crates/ctx-summarize/src/lib.rs
behavior: Crate root for ctx-summarize, the leaf-up context-tree summarization runner; declares the module layering and re-exports nothing beyond the modules themselves.
edit_notes:
  - Prompt text lives in external `prompts/` files loaded at runtime by runner/agent, not embedded in source; do not add prompt strings here.
  - Layering is cli (argv/io) -> runner (pure orchestration) -> fs/agent (seams); new code must respect this direction, e.g. runner must not depend on cli.
  - `intent.md` is deliberately never written by this crate; do not add that behavior without updating this doc comment.
functions:
invariants:
external_deps: